refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public voidAMQPExchange::delete
 stringexchange_nameNULL



 Delete and exchange from the broker.


&warn.undocumented.func;

&reftitle.parameters;
exchange_name
El nombre del intercambio eliminar. Si el AMQPExchange objeto ya está asociado a un cambio existente y, a continuación exchange_name no se especifica, el intercambio vinculado a el objeto será AMQPExchange deleted.

  &reftitle.examples;



    AMQPExchange::delete ejemplo


<?php

/* Create a new connection */
$cnn = new AMQPConnection();

/* Create a new exchange */
$ex = new AMQPExchange($cnn);
$ex->declare('new_topic_exchange', AMQP_DURABLE | AMQP_AUTODELETE);

/* Delete the previous exchange */
$ex2 = new AMQPExchange($cnn);
$ex2->delete('new_topic_exchange');

?>
